{
  "3328780": {
    "name": "猎厨狂欢！SEDAP! (体验版）",
    "steam_appid": 3328780,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>开发者通知：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你好！请注意，当前的 SEDAP! 演示版仅支持本地合作模式。我们仍在开发在线多人游戏功能，预计将通过未来的演示版更新推出。如果你打算在两台电脑上进行合作游戏，建议使用 Steam 内建的 <strong>Remote Play Together</strong> 功能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328780/extras/da54dc610c8a0a0decbf34b9fee1affc.webp?t=1739441992\" width=600 height=45 /></span>两位有抱负的烹饪天才开了一辆流动餐车，前往卡雅岛—一个长期被遗弃的危险岛屿，那里有无数怪物和谜团。两人一起探索卡雅岛，寻找新的食谱和味道，同时逐渐揭开困扰这个地方的秘密面纱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328780/extras/da54dc610c8a0a0decbf34b9fee1affc.webp?t=1739441992\" width=600 height=45 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328780/extras/2e17ab3babcd0416180465b45ac1c4fc.avif?t=1739441992\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论单人还是与朋友一起，都可以开启你的烹饪冒险！ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索每个关卡以获取食材并准备食物订单，沿途面对可怕的野兽和危险的障碍。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328780/extras/6a06ab511078ad69faa5584929309608.poster.avif?t=1739441992\" width=800 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328780/extras/6a06ab511078ad69faa5584929309608.webm?t=1739441992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328780/extras/6a06ab511078ad69faa5584929309608.mp4?t=1739441992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328780/extras/a81250f133196f8ef380c88ab57fda31.avif?t=1739441992\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为厨师制作美食，或作为猎人狩猎食材并对抗可怕的生物。只有你们共同努力，才能维持生意的运转！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328780/extras/5a11108e73608030657522a4518ef781.poster.avif?t=1739441992\" width=800 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328780/extras/5a11108e73608030657522a4518ef781.webm?t=1739441992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328780/extras/5a11108e73608030657522a4518ef781.mp4?t=1739441992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328780/extras/99504295eaea22812f489ed22d047857.avif?t=1739441992\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个丰富而独特的东南亚风格的奇幻世界中冒险，磨练你的烹饪技能，揭开卡雅岛的秘密。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >岛上拥有各种截然不同的生物群落，每个群落都有自己的食物、烹饪方法和独特的野生动物，供玩家享受。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328780/extras/14b12b128b3b56adfca732f422bdc630.poster.avif?t=1739441992\" width=800 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328780/extras/14b12b128b3b56adfca732f422bdc630.webm?t=1739441992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328780/extras/14b12b128b3b56adfca732f422bdc630.mp4?t=1739441992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328780/extras/bb17a9d9cb0d3f8e130fad392fb7ecbf.avif?t=1739441992\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备各种在东南亚广受欢迎的菜肴，如菠萝炒饭、鸡饭、越南三明治和珍珠奶茶！ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你发现并掌握每道菜的烹饪方法，填满你的美食宝典！每个关卡都有大量等待端上的菜肴。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328780/extras/0a95554bdb70642e5561b1955d5b3ecd.poster.avif?t=1739441992\" width=800 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328780/extras/0a95554bdb70642e5561b1955d5b3ecd.webm?t=1739441992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328780/extras/0a95554bdb70642e5561b1955d5b3ecd.mp4?t=1739441992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328780/extras/c0e91ecdfe18d9df8b7f0a0817b78f52.avif?t=1739441992\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对卡雅岛的挑战时，装备自己以护身符、武器和器具。</p></li></ul>",
